Amplify the Impact of Your Ministry
Ready for your church to go live? 
Get Started









Live Video Streaming for Churches




You pour your heart into your ministry; wouldn’t it be great if there were a way for your message to touch more lives?
This is where BoxCast comes in.
By live video streaming and archiving your Sunday services, Bible studies, church meetings, weddings and funerals, you can connect with your members even when they can't be there.















Key Features




Simple
We realize Sundays are hectic - the last thing you need is another complicated task to worry about. BoxCast allows you to plug in your camera, schedule your broadcast and focus on what’s really important - your message. Our streaming platform does all the work for you.



Reliable
Count on picture-perfect video with no buffering, delivered to any device. Plus, you never have to worry about embarrassing ads popping up. Our dedicated customer support team monitors your broadcasts. If we ever notice a technical issue, we'll work with you to fix it.



Affordable
Take advantage of all our incredible standard features - unlimited streaming, multi-device compatibility, automatic archiving and unbeatable customer support - all for a price that's right for you.




Contact our sales team to learn more







