BoxCast Video Streaming for Associations











































Improve How You Reach and Involve Members
Ready to stream? 
Get Started

























Live Video Streaming for Associations



Engage members, attract prospective applicants, and earn revenue with BoxCast’s live video streaming platform. Professional member associations host amazing activities all year long. Events like annual conferences, monthly educational workshops, regional speaker panels, and board meetings provide an incredible amount of value.
Unfortunately, distance and cost prevent many people from participating in these events. Live streaming addresses this problem head-on, allowing organizations to better promote their events and serve their members.







With BoxCast's live video streaming platform, associations can:



Engage anyone, anywhere
Many people are unable to travel long distances to attend an event, no matter how much they’d like to. Live streaming your event gives those who can’t be there in person with the opportunity to participate from afar. 


Earn additional revenue
Many associations depend on the income their events provide. That’s why BoxCast’s built-in ticketing feature makes it easy to charge viewers on a pay-per-view basis. You can still generate revenue, even if participants can’t be there in person.




Innovate and adapt
Innovation doesn’t have to be expensive. BoxCast’s solution is not only affordable, but it’s a great way to set yourself apart. Members young and old will appreciate the flexibility live streaming provides them, and you won’t have to break your budget.


Create engaging content
Once your live stream is over, BoxCast will automatically provide you with the recorded video file. You can easily use this archived footage to create educational materials, on-demand offerings, and other content for resale, promotional marketing, or internal use.




 


Streaming Has Never Been So Easy






1
CAPTURE
BoxCast can acquire video from numerous sources including cameras, switchers and iOS devices.



2
DELIVER
BoxCast sends video to the cloud and optimizes it so that viewers anywhere can watch the stream live.



3
WATCH
BoxCast gives your viewers a professional experience on any device.










Key Features



Simple
BoxCast’s platform makes it easy to stream. Stream from any video camera with our plug-and-play setup, or from any iOS device. No tech team? No problem.


Reliable
When it comes to planning events, there are a lot of things to worry about. Your live stream shouldn’t be one of them. Our amazing customer support team is on call when you need them. We even proactively monitor broadcasts.


Affordable
BoxCast was founded on the belief that live streaming should be a possibility for anyone. Your organization is no exception. With BoxCast’s ticketing feature, streaming could even become a new revenue source.



Contact our sales team to learn more



 


